      "titleText": "The Filesystem",
      "titleColor": "#00ff41",
      "titleSize": 52,
      "subtitleText": "",
      "subtitleColor": "#2a6b3a",
      "bodyText": "The filesystem defines how data is organised, stored, and retrieved on a storage device. It is the logical structure that manages files and directories within a partition.",
